tions. We then consider the closed, model equation for the RDF given in\nZaichik \\& Alipchenkov (Phys. Fluids. 19:113308, 2007) and use this, together\nwith the results from our analysis, to predict the analytic form of the RDF in\nthe inertial range for ${St_r\\ll1}$, which, unlike that in the dissipation\nrange, is not scale-invariant. The results are in good agreement with direct...\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Nov 2014 23:31:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-06"}
